data.description: Welcome Home to this charming cape cod located in Greene Township just one mile from Interstate 81. You'll love the unique brick exterior and adorable front porch as soon as you pull in!  The long driveway and parking area allow for an abundance of convenience leading to your 2-car detached garage.  Be sure to walk the length of the yard as this property is nearly 1 full acre in size! Inside, you'll find an original kitchen that is cute as a button.  The main floor also hosts a separate dining room, large living room, front door entryway and half bathroom.  You'll love the hardwood floors and accents along with the wood burning fireplace to cuddle up next to!  Upstairs hosts a full bathroom and 3 bedrooms.  There is walk-up attic access from one of the bedrooms that allows for storage or other ideas!   The basement is unfinished, but includes a laundry area along with a small workshop and plenty of storage giving you additional space to use to your liking. If you think this could be the one, call today!
